### Guest Plugin API Tests

### 1. Guest Login (Auto-registration)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/plugin/guest/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "device_id": "test-device-123",
  "device_info": "Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64)"
}

### Save the token from response for next requests
@guestToken = {{login.response.body.data.token}}

### 2. Get Current Guest Info (Protected Route)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/plugin/guest/me
Authorization: Bearer {{guestToken}}

### 3. Guest Login from Another Device
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/plugin/guest/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "device_id": "mobile-device-456",
  "device_info": "Mozilla/5.0 (iPhone; CPU iPhone OS 14_0 like Mac OS X)"
}
